Good. You ready?

260
00:10:36.482 --> 00:10:37.779
Go!

261
00:10:43.690 --> 00:10:46.318
(Jack)
Go. Danny. Go! Go! Go!

262
00:10:52.765 --> 00:10:53.959
Whoa!

263
00:10:54.033 --> 00:10:55.898
Watch out! Watch out!

264
00:11:03.609 --> 00:11:04.701
I won!

265
00:11:04.844 --> 00:11:06.368
[all laughing]

266
00:11:06.546 --> 00:11:09.947
